{
  "stem": "23090.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Out of a tooth-- she was a year older than I was-- they couldn't do anything for her, so she-- she was running high fever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "She was just delirious with high fever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these appells would come every three hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They would chase you out of the barracks, into the barracks, which was happening with the women as well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So with her fever, she could not stand at the appells.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She could no longer stand up, so my aunts and my mother held her up so she could stand up and somehow overcome this-- this-- this-- this problem, this tooth abscess.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And finally, she succumbed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She could no longer keep her head up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she was detected by one of the guards, one of the women guards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they dragged her out of the formation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my mother knew where she was going.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my sister was crying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, she wanted her mother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm giving you this verbatim.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is not from somebody's-- my aunts, who are today alive, they are survivors.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were with her, so I'm giving it to you from my aunts, to me, and to this interview.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My mother looked at my aunts and she said, if I knew that my son was alive, maybe I would sacrifice my daughter, if I could think that I could see him.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "She said, since I don't know if he survived and I don't know if any of them survived, I'm not going to let my daughter go by herself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my mother would have survived because she was a-- she was a survivor, like my aunt did and my other one.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And with that, she bid my aunts goodbye and she went with my sister to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
